metadata.name: Checks - Team White
metadata.description:
This elemental matrix may or may not be notable. 

[Team White]

Each color is associated with the following principles and virtues:

White = Independency = Nobility

Black = Interdependency = Humility

Orange = Assertivity = Bravery

Blue = Receptivity = Curiosity

Red = Criticality = Responsibility

Green = Tolerancy = Sympathy

Yellow = Resiliency = Tenacity

Purple = Flexibility = Spontaneity
